# new-satellite

Scaffold a new reverberage satellite package under `reverberage/<name>`.

## Usage

```
/new-satellite <name> [--description <desc>] [--with-mcp]
```

## What it produces

Creates `reverberage/<name>` on GitHub and a local clone with:

```
<name>/
├── src/<name>/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── cli.py          # Typer CLI entry point
│   └── models.py       # Pydantic v2 models
├── tests/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   └── test_cli.py
├── pyproject.toml       # hatchling build, pip-installable
├── README.md
└── .gitignore
```

## Requirements

- `gh` CLI authenticated with write access to `reverberage` org
- Python >=3.11 available

## Options

- `--description` — Short description for pyproject.toml
- `--with-mcp` — Include MCP server scaffold (`mcp.py`, FastMCP pattern)
